 4 Dance|D3 \u2013 D4 Dance]]''\n| Guest\n| [[Mazhavil Manorama]]\n| Along with Abhirami Suresh\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''Smart Show''\n| Participant\n| [[Flowers (TV channel)|Flowers]]\n| Along with Abhirami Suresh <br>Opposite Stephen Devassy & Merin Gregory\n|-\n|\n| ''Mylanchi Little Champions''\n| Guest Singer\n| [[Asianet (TV channel)|Asianet]]\n| \n|-\n| 2017\n| ''Chat with Amrutha Suresh''\n| Guest\n| [[Kaumudy TV]]\n| Talk show\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''Varthakkappuram''\n| Guest\n| [[Asianet News]]\n| Talk show\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''Music Shots''\n| Singer\n| [[Manorama Online]]\n| \n|-\n|2017 || ''Miss & Mrs Kerala Beauty Pageant 2017'' || Performer || [[Kairali TV]] ||Alongside Amruthamgamaya band \n|-\n| 2017\n| ''Moodtapes''\n| Singer\n| [[Kappa TV]]\n| \n|-\n|2017 \n| ''Amruthamgamaya'' \n| Guest \n| [[News18 Kerala]] \n| Along with Abhirami Suresh\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''The Happiness Project''\n| Guest\n| [[Kappa TV]]\n| Talk show\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''Paadaam Namukku Padaam''\n| Guest\n| [[Mazhavil Manorama]]\n| Along with Abhirami Suresh\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''Mazhavil Music Awards''\n| Herself\n| [[Mazhavil Manorama]]\n| Award ceremony; nominated for \"Minni Minni\" in ''[[June (film)|June]]''\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''Josh Talks''\n| Herself\n| [[Josh Talks]]\n| Talk show\n|-\n| 2020\n| [[Bigg Boss (Malayalam season 2)|''Bigg Boss'' (Malayalam season 2)]]\n| Herself\n| [[Asianet (TV channel)|Asianet]]\n| [[Reality TV]] competition; paired with Abhirami Suresh \n|}\n\n==Online appearances==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Network\n! class=\"unsortable\"| Notes\n|-\n| 2017 \n \t\t\n| ''How Well Do You Know'' \n \t\t\n| Guest \n \t\t\n| FWD TV Online \n \t\n| Chat show\n \t\n|-\n| 2017 \n \t\t\n| '' IndiaGlitz Malayalam Movies Interview\t'' \n \t\t\n| Guest \n \t\t\n| IndiaGlitz Online \n \t\n| Chat show\n \t\n|-\n| 2017 \n \t\t\n| '' Sensations Entertainment\t'' \n \t\t\n| Guest \n \t\t\n| Online\n \t\n| Talk show\n|-\n| 2019\n \t\t\n| ''Movie Man''\n \t\t\n| Herself\