ice|| \n|-\n|1999||''[[Garshom]]''||Noorja||Film Council Award\n|-\n|1997||''[[Janadhipathyam]]''||Indira Menon||Dubbed in [[Tamil language|Tamil]] as ''Makkal Thilagam'' and Telugu as \"City Commissioner\"\n|-\n|1997||''[[Kottapurathe Koottukudumbam]]''||Sree Devi|| \n|-\n|1996||''[[Kazhakam]]''||Radha||Fourth State Award, FilmFare award\n|-\n|1995||''[[Simhavalan Menon]]''||Geethanjali|| \n|-\n|1995|| ''[[Spadikam]]''||Thulasi|| \n|-\n|1995||''[[Thovalapookkal]]''||Chempakam|| \n|-\n|1994||''[[Bharya (1994 film)|Bharya]]''||Shailaja|| \n|-\n|1994||''[[The City (1994 film)|The City]]''||Dr. Jyothy||Dubbed in [[Telugu language|Telugu]] as ''The City''\n|-\n|1994||''[[Kudumba Visesham]]''||Geetha||\n|-\n|1994||''[[Pidakkozhi Koovunna Noottandu]]''||Bhagyarekha/Sujatha||Writer & Producer\n|-\n|1994||''[[Sukham Sukhakaram]]''||Susie|| \n|-\n|1993||''[[Palayam (film)|Palayam]]''||Jancy|| \n|-\n|1993||''[[Aayirappara]]''||Parvathy||Dubbed in Telugu as ''Ankuram''\n|-\n|1993||''[[Ithu Manju Kaalam]]''||Aswathy & Revathy (double role)||\n|-\n|1993||''[[Injakkadan Mathai & Sons]]''||Sherley|| \n|-\n|1993||''[[Kalippattam]]''||Saroja|| \n|-\n|1993||''[[Koushalam]]''||Maya Devi|| \n|-\n|1993||''[[Mithunam (1993 film)|Mithunam]]''||Sulochana|| \n|-\n|1993||''[[Narayam]]''||Gayathri|| \n|-\n|1993||''[[Sthreedhanam]]''||Vidhya||\n|-\n|1993||''[[Venkalam]]''||Thankamani|| \n|-\n|1992||''[[Kizhakkan Pathrose]]''||Chala Mary|| \n|-\n|1992||''[[Yodha (1992 film)|Yodha]]''||Damayanthi||Dubbed in Tamil, Telugu, [[Hindi]] as ''Asokan'', ''Yoddha'', ''Dharam Yoddha'' respectively \n|-\n|1992||''[[Aham (film)|Aham]]''||Renjini|| \n|-\n|1992||''[[Ardram]]''||Mary|| \n|-\n|1992||''[[Aparatha]]''||Prabha||\n|-\n|1992||''[[Ente Ponnu Thampuran]]''||Kavitha||\n|-\n|1992||''[[Malootty]]''||Raji||Dubbed in Tamil\n|-\n|1992||''[[My Dear Muthachan]]''||Clara||\n|-\n|1992||''[[Ponnaramthottathe Rajavu]]''||Radhika|| \n|-\n|1992||''[[Sathyapathijna]]''||Sreekutty|| \n|-\n|1992||''[[Simhadhwani]]''|