am]]''||Ammini||\n|-\n|2002||''[[Game (2002 film)|Game]]''||Janaki||\n|-\n|2002||''[[Thamizh]]''||Kalaiselvi|| \n|-\n|2003||''[[Three Roses]]''||Chandralekha||\n|-\n|2003|| ''[[Thennavan]]''||Pushpalatha||Dubbed in Telugu as ''Election Commissioner''\n|-\n|2003||''[[Success (2003 film)|Success]]''||Radha||\n|-\n|2005||''[[Anbe Aaruyire (2005 film)|Anbe Aaruyire]]''||Maami||\n|-\n|2006||''Desiya Paravai''||Malini||\n|-\n|2007||''[[Malaikottai]]''||Kamala||Dubbed in Telugu as ''Bhayya''\n|-\n|2007||''[[Kalakkura Chandru]]''||Host||Dubbed in Telugu as ''Chandru''\n|-\n|2009||''[[Siva Manasula Sakthi]]''||Kalyani||Edison Film Award\n|-\n|2009||''[[Vaamanan]]''||Divya's mother||\n|-\n|2009||''[[Peranmai]]''||Victoria||Dubbed in [[Hindi]] as ''Kasam Hindustan Ki''\n|-\n|2010||''[[Manmadan Ambu]]''||Mallika||Dubbed in Telugu as ''Manmadha Banam''\n|-\n|2011||''Doo''||Vasanth's mother||\n|-\n|2011||''[[Venghai]]''||Thangam||Dubbed in [[Hindi]] as ''Meri Taqat Mera Faisla'' and into Telugu as ''Simha Putrudu''\n|-\n|2011||''[[Vedi (film)|Vedi]]''|| Dr. Radha Jeyachandran||Dubbed in [[Hindi]] as ''The Fighter Mard No.1''\n|-\n|2012||''Sollithara Naanirukkiren''||-||\n|-\n|2013||''[[Vanakkam Chennai]]''||Chandra|| \n|-\n|2014||''[[Un Samayal Arayil]]''||Chechi|| \n|-\n|2014||''[[Vizhi Moodi Yosithaal]]''||KG's mother||\n|-\n|2014||''Pechiyakka Marumagan''||Pechiyakka|| \n|-\n|2015||''[[Tamizhuku En Ondrai Azhuthavum]]''||Vasanth's mother||\n|-\n|2015||''[[Uthama Villain]]''||Varalakshmi||Dubbed into Malayalam as ''Uthama Villain''\n|-\n|2015||''[[Savaale Samaali]]''||Urvashi|| \n|-\n|2015||''[[Size Zero (film)|Inji Iduppazhagi]]''||Rajeswari||\n|-\n|2015||''[[India Pakistan]]''||Kathik's mother||\n|-\n|2016||''[[Adida Melam]]''||Annapoorniyamma||\n|-\n|2016||''[[Unnodu Ka]]''||Rajalatchumi|| \n|-\n|2016||''[[Pencil (film)|Pencil]]''||Rajeshwari|| \n|-\n|2016||''[[Vaaimai]]''||Narayani|| \n|-\n|2016||''[[Meen Kuzhambum Mann Paanaiyum]]''||Pavithra's mother||\n|-\n|2016||''[[Bayam Oru Payanam]]''||Abhinya's mother|| Dubbed in Hindi as ''Kaher Ek Raat''\n|-\n|2016||''[[Kadavul Irukaan Kumaru]]''||Gomathi Gopalakrishnan||Dubbed into Telugu as ''Chennai Chinnodu''\n|-\n|2017||''[[Shivalinga (2017 film)|Shivalinga]]''||Arasuvai Annalakshmi||Dubbed in Hindi as ''Kanchana Returns''\n|-\n|2017||''[[Magalir Mattum (2017 film)|Magalir Mattum]]''||Gomatha||Dubbed into Malayalam as ''Mayavarnangal''<br>Nominated for Film Fare Award 2019-Best Supporting Actress\n|-\n|2017||''Palli Paruvathile''||Sarangan's wife|| \n|-\n|2018||''[[Koothan]]''||Kalairasi||\n|-\n|2019||''[[Dhilluku Dhuddu 2]]'' || Chakra Mahadevi ||\n|-\n|2019||''[[Pottu (film)|Pottu]]'' ||Mohana || Dubbed in Telugu as ''Bottu'' and in Hindi as ''Bindi''\n|-\n|2020||''[[Oh Andha Naatkal]]'' ||Thripurasundari ||\n|-\n|2020||''Mappilai Vinayagar'' ||- ||\n|-\n|2020||''Daavu'' ||- ||\n|-\n|2020||''Thiruvalar Panjangam'' || -||\n|-\n|2020||''Kopperundevi'' ||- ||\n|-\n|2020||''Mookuthi Amman'' || -||\n|-\n|2020||''Nenjamellam Kaadhal'' || ||\n|-\n|2020||''Asura Guru'' || ||\n|-\n|2020||''[[Soorarai Pottru]]''|| || Dubbed into Telugu as ''Aakasham Nee Haddhu Ra''\n|}\n\n====Kannada films====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! '''Year''' !! '''Title''' !! '''Role''' !! '''Notes'''\n|-\n|2018||''Buddhu''||-||Filming\n|-\n|2018||''Limit''||-||Filming\n|-\n|2018||''Sur Sur Batti''||Baddi Gowramma||\n|-\n|2016||''[[Jaggu Dada]]''||Jaggu Dada's mother||Dubbed in Hindi as ''Khatarnak Khiladi 3''\n|-\n|2016||''[[Shivalinga (2016 film)|Shivalinga]]''||Anusooya||Dubbed in Hindi & Telugu as ''Shivalinga''\n|-\n|2015||''[[Ram-Leela (2015 Kannada film)|Ram-Leela]]''||Baby|| \n|-\n|2014||''[[Oggarane (film)|Oggarane]]''||Beautician|| \n|-\n|2014||''[[Brahma (2014 film)|Brahma]]''||-||\n|-\n|2012||''Golmal Gayathri''||Gayathri||\n|-\n|2010||''Preeti Hungama''||Police Inspector||\n|-\n|2009||''[[Raaj the Showman]]''||Herself||Special appearance\n|-\n|2009||''Iniya''||Kamala|| \n|-\n|2008||''Arjun''||Vishalakshi Jayasimha|| \n|-\n|2008||''[[Nee Tata Naa Birla]]''||Cook|| \n|-\n|2005||''[[Rama Shama Bhama]]''||Bhamamani||\n|-\n|2003||''Vijaya Dashami''||Parvathy||Dubbed into Telugu as ''Pedamma Talli''\n|-\n|2003||''[[Katthegalu Saar Katthegalu]]''||Urmila|| \n|-\n|2001||''[[Kothigalu Saar Kothigalu]]''||Alamelu|| \n|-\n|2000||''[[Yaarige Saluthe Sambala]]''||Suguna|| \n|-\n|1999||''[[Habba]]''||Ambi's wife||Dubbed in Hindi as ''Kalyug Ka Pandav''\n|-\n|1996||''[[Jeevanadhi]]''||Dr.Priyadarshini|| \n|-\n|1988||''[[December 31 (film)|31 December]]''||Radha|| \n|-\n|1988||''[[New Delhi (1988 Kannada film)|New Delhi]]''||Uma||\n|-\n|1987||''[[Premaloka]]''||Rohini||Dubbed into Telugu as ''Premalokam''\n|-\n|1987||''[[Anthima Ghatta]]''||Sunitha|| \n|-\n|1986||''[[Ee Jeeva Ninagagi]]''||Rohini|| \n|-\n|1986||''[[Sathya Jyothi]]'' ||Sujatha||\n|-\n|1985||''[[Shabash Vikram]]''||Gayatri||Dubbed in Tamil as ''Kadamai Enathu Udamai''\n|-\n|1985||''[[Naanu Nanna Hendthi]]''||Urvashi|| \n|-\n|1984||''[[Shravana Banthu]]''||Urvashi/Mary/Saraswathi|| \n|-\n|1982||''Shankar Sundar''|||| \n|-\n|1980||''Akhanda Brahmacharigalu''||||\n|-\n|1980||''Nyaya Neethi Dharma''|||| \n|}\n\n====Telugu films====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! '''Year''' !! '''Title''' !! '''Role''' !! '''Notes'''\n|-\n|1984||''[[Rustum]]''||Padma||Dubbed into Tamil as ''Machachakkalai''\n|-\n|1984||''Ammayiloo! Preminchandi!''||Film actress||\n|-\n|1984||''Udhdhandudu''||-||\n|-\n|1985||''Kala Rudrudu''||-||\n|-\n|1985||''[[Bhale Thammudu (1985 film)|Bhale Thammudu]]''||Latha||\n|-\n|1986||''[[Jeevana Poratam]]''||Mallika||\n|-\n|1988||''[[Anthima Theerpu (1988 film)|Anthima Theerpu]]''||Uma||\n|-\n|1989||''[[Chettu Kinda Pleader]]''||Sujatha||\n|-\n|1999||''Kaama''||-||\n|-\n|2000||''[[Vijayaramaraju]]''||Rani||\n|-\n|2002||''[[Sandade Sandadi]]''||Lakshmi||\n|-\n|2002||''[[Allari Ramudu]]''||Collector||Dubbed in [[Hindi]] as ''Main Hoon Khuddar''\n|-\n|2004||''[[Intlo Srimathi Veedhilo Kumari]]''||Anjali Murthy|| \n|-\n|2004||''[[Swarabhishekam]]'' ||Rukminiamma||\n|-\n|2005||''[[Chakram (2005 film)|Chakram]]''||Lakshmi||Dubbed in [[Hindi]] as ''Chakran''\n|-\n|2010||''[[Maro Charitra (2010 film)|Maro Charitra]]''||Durga||\n|-\n|2014||''[[Brahma (2014 film)|Brahma]]''||-||\n|-\n|2014||''[[Un Samayal Arayil|Ulavacharu Biryani]]''||Beautician|| \n|-\n|2015||''[[Jil (film)|Jil]]''||Jai's aunt||\n|-\n|2015||''[[Size Zero (film)|Size Zero]]''||Rajeswari||\n|-\n|2016||''[[Express Raja]]''||Vasanthakokila (Uthaman's mother)||\n|-\n|2016||''[[Sardaar Gabbar Singh]]''||Madhumati||Dubbed in Hindi as ''Sardaar Gabbar Singh''\n|-\n|2016||''[[Manamantha]]''||Lakshmi||\n|-\n|2019||''[[Oh Baby (film)|Oh Baby]]''||Sulochana||Dubbed in Tamil with the same title\n|-\n|2019||''[[Raju Gari Gadhi 3]]''||Rajamatha ||\n|-\n|}\n\n====Hindi films====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|- \n! '''Year''' !! '''Title''' !! '''Role''' !! '''Notes'''\n|-\n|1988||''[[New Delhi (1988 Hindi film)|New Delhi]]''||Uma||\n|-\n|}\n\n===Voice Credit===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|- \n! '''Year''' !! '''Title''' !! '''Role''' !! '''Voice to''' !!Language\n|-\n|2002||''[[Nandanam (film)|Nandanam]]''||Janaki||[[Kalarenjini]]||[[Malayalam]]\n|-\n|2002||''Panchatantram''||Mrs. Ammini Iyappan Nair||Herself||[[Telugu language|Telugu]]\n|-\n|2012||''Chellathambi''||Thamara||Herself||[[Tamil language|Tamil]]\n|-\n|2015||''[[Uttama Villain]]''||Varalaxmi||Herself||Telugu\n|-\n|2016||''Namadhu''|| Lakshmi||Herself||Tamil\n|-\n|2016||''[[Pencil (film)|Pencil]]''||Rajeswari||Herself||Telugu\n|-\n|2017||''[[Shivalinga (2017 film)|Shivalanga]]''||Arasuvai Annalakshmi||Herself||Telugu\n|-\n|2018||''[[Inba Twinkle Lilly|Itly]]''||Lilly||[[Kalpana (Malayalam actress)|Kalpana]] ||Tamil\n|-\n|2019||''[[Oh! Baby]]''||Sulochana||Herself ||Tamil\n|-\n|}\n\n==Other works==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Film !! Role!! Language !!Note\n|-\n|1992||''[[Utsavamelam]]''||Story Writer||Malayalam||\n|-\n|1994