a||\n|-\n|1993||''[[Venkalam]]''||Thankamani|| \n|-\n|1992||''[[Kizhakkan Pathrose]]''||Chala Mary|| \n|-\n|1992||''[[Yodha (1992 film)|Yodha]]''||Damayanthi||Dubbed in Tamil, Telugu, [[Hindi]] as ''Asokan'', ''Yoddha'', ''Dharam Yoddha'' respectively \n|-\n|1992||''[[Aham (film)|Aham]]''||Renjini|| \n|-\n|1992||''[[Ardram]]''||Mary|| \n|-\n|1992||''[[Aparatha]]''||Prabha||\n|-\n|1992||''[[Ente Ponnu Thampuran]]''||Kavitha||\n|-\n|1992||''[[Malootty]]''||Raji||Dubbed in Tamil\n|-\n|1992||''[[My Dear Muthachan]]''||Clara||\n|-\n|1992||''[[Ponnaramthottathe Rajavu]]''||Radhika|| \n|-\n|1992||''[[Sathyapathijna]]''||Sreekutty|| \n|-\n|1992||''[[Simhadhwani]]''||Jayasree||Dubbed in Telugu as ''Simha Dhwani''\n|-\n|1992||''[[Snehasagaram]]''||Treesa|| \n|-\n|1992||''[[Soorya Gayathri]]''||Rugmini|| \n|-\n| 1992||''[[Thiruthalvaadi]]''||Lathika|| \n|-\n|1992||''[[Utsava Melam]]''||Kanaka Prabha||Story\n|-\n|1991||''[[Bhoomika]]''||Radha|| \n|-\n|1991||''[[Inspector Balram]]''||Preethi Krishna Mathur||Dubbed in Tamil as ''Police Inna Police''\n|-\n|1991||''[[Koodikazhcha]]''||Alice|| \n|-\n|1991||''[[Kanalkkattu]]''||Aasha|| \n|-\n|1991||''[[Bharatham]]''||Devi||Third State Award\n|-\n|1991||''[[Chanchattam (1991 film)|Chanchattam]]''||Yamuna|| \n|-\n|1991||''[[Kadinjool Kalyanam]]''||Hrudayakumari||Third State Award\n|-\n|1991||''[[Kakkathollayiram]]''||Revathy||Third State Award\n|-\n|1991||''[[Mukha Chithram]]''||Savithrikutty/Lakshmikutty||Third State Award\n|-\n|1991||''[[Souhridham]]''||Shiny|| \n|-\n|1991||''[[Vishnulokam]]''||Kasthoori|| \n|-\n|1990||''[[Arhatha]]''||Aswathy|| \n|-\n|1990||''[[Lal Salam (1990 film)|Lal Salam]]''||Annamma||Dubbed in Telugu as ''Nayakudu''\n|-\n|1990||''[[Kouthuka Varthakal]]''||Aswathy|| \n|-\n|1990||''[[Nanma Niranjavan Srinivasan]]''||Chandrika ||\n|-\n|1990||''[[Thalayanamanthram]]''||Kanchana||Second State Award\n|-\n|1990||''[[Thoovalsparsham]]''||Maya|| \n|-\n|1990||''[[Veena Meettiya Vilangukal]]''||Geetha|| \n|-\n|1990||''[[