akkili Karayarilla]]''||Devika|| \n|-\n|1986||''[[Manasilloru Manimuthu]]''||Radhika||\n|-\n|1986||''[[Kshamichu Ennoru Vakku]]''||Rajani|| \n|-\n|1986||''[[Sukhamo Devi]]''||Devi|| \n|-\n|1986||''[[Mizhineerpoovukal]]''||Aswathy|| \n|-\n|1986||''[[Sunil Vayassu 20]]''||Premalatha|| \n|-\n|1986||''[[Yuvajanotsavam]]''||Sindhu|| \n|-\n|1985||''[[Karimpinpoovinakkare]]''||Chandrika|| \n|-\n|1985||''[[Pathamudayam]]''||Valsala|| \n|-\n|1985||''[[Daivatheorthu]]''||Nani|| \n|-\n|1985||''[[Nirakkoottu]]''||Sasikala||\n|-\n|1985||''[[Ente Ammu Ninte Thulasi Avarude Chakki]]''||Thulasi|| \n|-\n|1984||''[[Ethirppukal]]''||Sudha|| \n|-\n|1983||''[[Hello Madras Girl]]''||Latha||\n|-\n|1982||''Yaagam''||||\n|-\n|1980||''[[Dwik Vijayam]]''||Dance Student||\n|-\n|1979||''[[Sayoojyam]]''||Child artist(Song Scene)||\n|-\n|1979||''[[Kathirmandapam]]''||Child artist|| \n|-\n|1979||''[[Sikharangal]]''||Child artist||\n|-\n|1977||''[[Vidarunna Mottukal]]''||Child artist||\n|-\n|}\n\n====Tamil films====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! '''Year''' !! '''Title''' !! '''Role''' !! '''Notes'''\n|-\n|1983||''[[Mundhanai Mudichu]]''||Parimalam||Tamil Nadu State Award<br/> Dubbed into Telugu as ''Vaadante Pelli''\n|-\n|1983||''[[Apoorva Sahodarigal]]''||Rosy|| \n|-\n|1984||''[[Dhavani Kanavugal]]''||Film actress||\n|-\n|1984||''[[Komberi Mookan]]''||Priya|| \n|-\n|1984||''[[Nerupukkul Eeram]]''||Ganga||Dubbed into Telugu as ''Nippu Rava''\n|-\n|1984||''[[Oh Maane Maane]]''||Stella||\n|-\n|1984||''[[Ambigai Neril Vanthaal]]''||Latha||\n|-\n|1984||''[[Anbe Odi Vaa]]''||Seetha||Mohan\n|-\n|1984||''[[Ezhuthatha Sattangal]]''||Meena||\n|-\n|1984||''[[Vai Pandal]]''||Santhi||\n|-\n|1984||''Vengaiyin Mainthan''||Yamuna||\n|-\n|1984||''[[Oorukku upadesam|Oorukku Upadesam]]''||Janaki||\n|-\n|1984||''Shanthi Mugurtham''||Santhi|| \n|-\n|1984||''Neram Nalla Neram''||Vadivu||\n|-\n|1984||''Ninaivukal Maraivathillai''||-||\n|-\n|1984||''Vamsa Vilakku''||-||\n|-\n|1984||''Vellai Pura Ondru''||-|| \n|-\n